Hi Steve,

I know it&#39;s been brutal up your way. I don&#39;t know how you are getting around in all that. I think most of the US is having a tougher winter than normal. Down here they closed many businesses and all the schools because it &quot;might&quot; snow a few weeks ago. I&#39;m originally from NYC, so that kind of thing really blows my mind.

Where I am now only gets snow once every 5 years or so, but this year was the second year in a row that we got some. It usually doesn&#39;t get below freezing at night until February, but this year it started in December. 

I&#39;ll keep my eyes open for your email.

~Draiga


